7a35631305a8b2bee4e5c3da2897d47c9b866d02ad2395d51498500f34b78f2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "3dec495d-5aa1-41c2-b97a-81ca136cb8e5", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "063f76155b1e37c6d7fc01a35fe3481e2634137e71bc4c6b69186419cf08d1c1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "If Confidential Information is in written form, the Disclosing Party shall label or stamp the materials with the word \"Confidential\" or some similar warning. If Confidential Information is transmitted orally, the Disclosing Party shall promptly provide writing indicating that such oral communication constituted Confidential Information.2. Exclusions from Confidential Information .", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 791, "end_char_idx": 1174, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "3dec495d-5aa1-41c2-b97a-81ca136cb8e5": {"__data__": {"id_": "3dec495d-5aa1-41c2-b97a-81ca136cb8e5", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "70873dac-84ba-4ba6-b52d-b9b3ece89821", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6fc3648c81c267b58d1012429838b7edb4485edad5b08a2f539c7700a5cb9cd2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "f65d539f-2866-4ad5-8ae8-f3e2e0b6ee87", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0a5782b263d27342a6eadb548180dbdccbb0454a194d4741199141bc493b8979", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "effc543e-164d-4683-bfac-1127e137f763", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4c48a0eae991f3c23a196687a114bce54354d040703eae27e160e7d9b7bf3839", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Receiving Party's obligations under this Agreement do not extend to information that is: (a) publicly known at the time of disclosure or subsequently becomes publicly known through no fault of the Receiving Party; (b) discovered or created by the Receiving Party before disclosure by Disclosing Party; (c) learned by the Receiving Party through legitimate means other than from the Disclosing Party or Disclosing Party's representatives;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1177, "end_char_idx": 1614, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "effc543e-164d-4683-bfac-1127e137f763": {"__data__": {"id_": "effc543e-164d-4683-bfac-1127e137f763", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "70873dac-84ba-4ba6-b52d-b9b3ece89821", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6fc3648c81c267b58d1012429838b7edb4485edad5b08a2f539c7700a5cb9cd2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "3dec495d-5aa1-41c2-b97a-81ca136cb8e5", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "063f76155b1e37c6d7fc01a35fe3481e2634137e71bc4c6b69186419cf08d1c1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "658cfc07-b247-4460-9a6a-6eb8f494e9d2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3af87640e4d077ffc9cd2613f3bf9cfd83a63870fcea3b84d6a263370d8cf49b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "or (d) is disclosed by Receiving Party with Disclosing Party's prior written approval.\n\n3. Obligations of Receiving Party . Receiving Party shall hold and maintain the Confidential Information in strictest confidence for the sole and exclusive benefit of the Disclosing Party.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1615, "end_char_idx": 1891, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "658cfc07-b247-4460-9a6a-6eb8f494e9d2": {"__data__": {"id_": "658cfc07-b247-4460-9a6a-6eb8f494e9d2", "embedding": null, "metada