l Information no longer qualifies as a trade secret or until Disclosing Party sends Receiving Party written notice releasing Receiving Party from this Agreement, whichever occurs first.Copyright \u00a9 2018 NonDisclosureAgreement.com. All Rights Reserved.Page 1 of 2\n5. Relationships .", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2700, "end_char_idx": 3193, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "04af7453-d3b0-4fec-891a-bf90af5912f2": {"__data__": {"id_": "04af7453-d3b0-4fec-891a-bf90af5912f2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "70873dac-84ba-4ba6-b52d-b9b3ece89821", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6fc3648c81c267b58d1012429838b7edb4485edad5b08a2f539c7700a5cb9cd2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "1a0aa7e1-3227-4e6a-a464-9fcb56d0fbb3", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9381133496799519bdcb556ef56d8af24a3a99d7b43ec2e751ee50aa27802449", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "579411f2-37f1-47fd-9b41-9e16a907bf5b", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3862ab8f7837d0331af5c401b088b2771d47d1aa62692c1ff16181db19cef7db", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Nothing contained in this Agreement shall be deemed to constitute either party a partner, joint venture or employee of the other party for any purpose.6. Severability . If a court finds any provision of this Agreement invalid or unenforceable, the remainder of this Agreement shall be interpreted so as best to affect the intent of the parties.7. Integration .", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3196, "end_char_idx": 3556, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "579411f2-37f1-47fd-9b41-9e16a907bf5b": {"__data__": {"id_