 "start_char_idx": 4455, "end_char_idx": 4489, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "d4f25360-e72a-4473-b15a-8ab568afed0c": {"__data__": {"id_": "d4f25360-e72a-4473-b15a-8ab568afed0c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "70873dac-84ba-4ba6-b52d-b9b3ece89821", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6fc3648c81c267b58d1012429838b7edb4485edad5b08a2f539c7700a5cb9cd2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "9dd82be7-40bf-4100-beb4-44ab05312843", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a041d89b538b12a1b998ea494bdf4f1ce1930d89c15b5f2ccf7362ddc3f8034a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "41eceb70-c457-4f98-b341-8ac4b21269ad", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7492f5264a88fb22965d44200a3609326f184c936c07597f8b552180ad6a171e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "An individual who files a lawsuit for retaliation by an employer for reporting a suspected violation of law may disclose the trade secret to the attorney of the individual and use the trade secret information in the court proceeding, if the individual (i) files any document containing the trade secret under seal; and (ii) does not disclose the trade secret, except pursuant to court order.This Agreement and each party's obligations shall be binding on the representatives, assigns and successors of such party.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4492, "end_char_idx": 5005, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "41eceb70-c457-4f98-b341-8ac4b21269ad": {"__data__": {"id_": "41eceb70-c457-4f98-b341-8ac4b21269ad", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationship